LX_CG_SU          775 ; mm ! X distance SU CG is behind sprung mass origin [I]
Y_CG_SU             0 ; mm ! Y coordinate of SU CG [I]
M_SU           251.54 ; kg ! Mass of unladen sprung mass (SU) [I]
IXX_SU           5.28 ; kg-m2 ! Roll inertia for unladen sprung mass [I]
IYY_SU          56.88 ; kg-m2 ! Pitch inertia for SU [I]
IZZ_SU          76.97 ; kg-m2 ! Yaw inertia for SU [I]
IXY_SU              0 ; kg-m2 ! [D] XY product of inertia for SU [I]
IXZ_SU           0.82 ; kg-m2 ! XZ product of inertia for SU [I]
IYZ_SU              0 ; kg-m2 ! [D] YZ product of inertia for SU [I]

! N_PAYLOADS        0 ! No. of payloads attached to this sprung mass (read only)

HT_SM            1500 ; mm ! [D] Reference height of sprung mass (maybe for target)
LEN_SM           4000 ; mm ! [D] Reference length of sprung mass (maybe for target)
WID_SM           1600 ; mm ! [D] Reference width of sprung mass (maybe for target)
LX_F_SM          1000 ; mm ! [D] Length from front to control pt (maybe for target)

