! Simcenter Tire MF-Tyre/MF-Swift model: set context in VS model for axle 1, left side
IAXLE  1
ISIDE  1
! Simcenter Tire MF-Tyre/MF-Swift property file and DLL location
DELFT_TYRE_DLL 
DELFT_TYRE_SW   31124 ! Operating mode of Simcenter Tire MF-Tyre/MF-Swift model
DELFT_TYRE_TVM      0 ! Temperature mode of Simcenter Tire MF-Tyre/MF-Swift model
DELFT_TYRE_FREQ  1000 ! Solver frequency [Hz] of Simcenter Tire MF-Tyre/MF-Swift
                      ! model
DELFT_TYRE_INIT


